---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Knowledge Systems | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="AI-powered knowledge systems that turn organisational documents, research, models, and data into searchable decision intelligence."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">Knowledge Systems</p>
      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        Turn institutional knowledge into intelligence.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI helps organisations transform reports, policies, research, datasets, technical documents, and operational knowledge into searchable, explainable, and actionable intelligence.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">The problem</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Valuable knowledge is often difficult to use.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Most organisations hold large volumes of reports, datasets, policies, technical documents, meeting papers, and historical analyses.
          </p>
          <p>
            The challenge is rarely collecting information. The challenge is finding the right information at the right time and understanding how it applies to a decision.
          </p>
          <p>
            PrincipalAI creates knowledge systems that make institutional knowledge easier to find, compare, explain, and apply.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">Core capabilities</p>
        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Connect information to decisions.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Evidence retrieval</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Locate relevant information across large collections of documents, reports, datasets, and knowledge sources.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Knowledge synthesis</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Compare, summarise, and integrate information from multiple sources into structured responses.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Organisational memory</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Preserve institutional knowledge and make it available beyond individual projects, teams, and staff members.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Decision support</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Connect evidence directly to operational, strategic, technical, and policy decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">Example applications</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            AI knowledge systems for evidence-heavy work.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Research intelligence for literature, evidence reviews, and technical analysis.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Policy intelligence across legislation, guidance, consultation material, and reports.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Technical knowledge systems for infrastructure, operations, and project documentation.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Climate, health, energy, and geospatial intelligence connected to domain-specific models.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">How it works in practice</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Ask a question. Get a grounded answer.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5">
            “What evidence exists on the relationship between transport accessibility and employment outcomes?”
          </p>
          <p>
            The system searches relevant knowledge sources, identifies supporting evidence, extracts key findings, compares sources, and generates a structured response with references.
          </p>
          <p>
            This reduces manual search time and improves the consistency of evidence-based analysis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">Why PrincipalAI</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Built for knowledge-intensive organisations.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Many AI tools focus on generating content. PrincipalAI focuses on helping organisations use what they already know.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our knowledge systems combine AI, search, organisational content, technical expertise, modelling outputs, and decision-support frameworks.
          </p>
          <p>
            The result is an intelligence environment that improves consistency, productivity, and decision quality.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Make your organisation’s knowledge accessible.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about AI-powered knowledge systems for research, policy, infrastructure, climate, health, and operational decision-making.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
